Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:23.21,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}褪色的景致 隨著風兒逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:31.01,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,往日記憶 悄悄甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:37.93,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,走在熟悉的路上卻無法回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:43.89,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}最初的謊言 最後的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:57.45,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}那天許下的誓言早已崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:04.71,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,只留下激昂虛幻的記憶碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:12.67,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們一同從這夢境中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:18.89,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}這份思念 也不會被忘記 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:27.69,OpeningCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}懷念的往昔照亮今天的我
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:21.86,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}那時還年幼的我 抬頭仰望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:28.28,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,發現天空真的很遼闊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:32.74,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人 用雙手保護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:38.67,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經認真的這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:50.14,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有長高 我為此而悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:53.43,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,也曾無數次伸展手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:23:00.78,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,卻還是無法觸及 那無比寬廣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:06.69,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻沒有一絲懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:11.62,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,始終堅信那美好的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:14.91,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,也曾有過悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:22.29,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,亦會忍不住落下 大滴大滴的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:33.39,EndingCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}但是我堅信 那時我的眼中有著無比的光輝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛忽然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像迫使你們作出了不愉快的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然你們想找諾魯布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該知道那裡遲早會成為必經之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全被你看穿了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:02:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之德·希耶羅對你們來說是個重要的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是碰巧啊 碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然對我們補陀落來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是通往Great Wall所必經的蕩滌靈魂之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對所有造訪者來說 那裡也同時是抉擇之門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抉擇之門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paper Moon Shine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全系統進入停泊狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂魄干涉器的狀態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定位系統不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在這麼顯眼的地方反正也無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎一直保持點火 隨時可以起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也不準備在這兒久留吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他也想盡快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下那老婆婆之後 我想一定很快就會走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒忘帶什麼東西吧 再確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 雖然不成敬意…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說 請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許有一天會用得著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時要是沒有的話會很麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願不會碰上用得著它的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願無上的光明等候著各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 多吉哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是你哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 終於做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的新滑空板 帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:03:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 也不知道幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完這個就起飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德這麼說的 有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德? 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的波浪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德說過只要有好波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪裡都會去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德還真是反覆無常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆就在這裡下船了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就說好到這裡為止的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 你去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去把滑空板拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在加水的這段時間先在這裡滑滑空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒變化 現在正在補給飲用水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成之後立刻出發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了這麼好的波浪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對只為波浪而生的你來說真是少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又算怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛 有意見麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 霍蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 只是你不去滑空麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑空?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個家伙可已經先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 霍蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的波浪真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼好的滑空點居然什麼人也沒有 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對、對不起 水還沒加完…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是問你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡的波浪很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次見到這麼棒的波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這廢墟也有利波浪的形成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道為什麼沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真想感謝上蒼造出了這麼好的滑空點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛莫名其妙就打我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有個理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 莫名其妙地連打兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽臉色好難看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為姐姐惹媽媽生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 是因為林克尿床了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒尿床呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木炭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還很新
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 最近才受過轟炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德 蘭頓他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎是嗎 那可真是災難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得奇怪麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡外表看來雖然只是房車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但裡面其實卻是修道場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修道場?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補陀落真的是反政府組織麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為學校的老師和同學都說不知道你們想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你們是可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白不瞭解的東西就是可怕的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點大家都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老婆婆看起來卻完全不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 光看外表是無法瞭解一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是只看外表的話並沒有很大差異
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果大家都能理解這一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也不會變成這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這塊古老的土地並不僅僅屬於人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我們卻在不穩定的珊瑚岩中打入無數樁子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試圖壓制它們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是課本上說如果不打樁固定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會發生地殼變動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼打樁固定之後就不會發生地殼變動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是囫圇吞棗地讀著某些人所展示的東西罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在天黑之前回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且尼爾瓦修在這裡很危險 你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼特地跑來集中在這種什麼都沒有的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是抉擇之門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抉擇之門?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修達德斯·德·希耶羅 天空之都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾以美麗聞名的補陀落之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管被如何破壞 這一點都不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是該走向通往Great Wall之路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是該繼續停留在這大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡的人都要被驅使作出某種選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是座這樣的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而卻一片狼藉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 幾年前的某一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊襲擊了這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們毀了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且屠殺了補陀落的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提普特裡 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西又出現了 那白色惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色惡魔?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓 我知道你在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很擔心你 快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡 來找我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滾 滾出這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 她做錯了什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人是劊子手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又曾經做錯了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼啊 優萊卡她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我真的曾經是軍隊的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定時轟炸要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定時轟炸?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的空中戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍空中戰艦正高速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現正在對德·希耶羅南部進行轟炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮座回轉還沒結束 無法發射主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調速輪安定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步調勉強一致了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍蘭德呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開909出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是去回收尼爾瓦修了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先走吧 叫他別遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家要對你做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明看起來都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我活該
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我活該
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被人這樣對待都是我自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 竟然對女孩子做這種事 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我活該
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我曾經在這裡殺了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殲滅這座城市的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們SOF接到的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOF? 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們所在的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的特殊部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說 難道月光州的前身是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 只要有命令就絕對執行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純粹的殺人部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣 傳言居然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有理由 只是純粹地執行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我作為自己存在的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那時的我 只有尼爾瓦修和霍蘭德可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 只要霍蘭德說要戰斗 我就去戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 那時候發現的孩子們就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅特爾 莫裡斯 林克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 難道指揮了那場作戰的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們SOF小隊的隊長 是霍蘭德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 但是 那也是沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那時候在戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你又是軍人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也還在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所做的不是遊戲也不是運動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的戰斗 人類受到傷害 甚至死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能你沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蘭頓 你也在參與其中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參與這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會回來麼 媽媽會回來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 現在霍蘭德正去接她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 媽媽會回來?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 霍蘭德從來沒說過謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 偏偏在這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們決定無論用怎樣的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要補償我們所犯下的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為此我們就首先要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須活下去完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我們會不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了要我戰斗才把我帶來的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因為如果你不在 尼爾瓦修就不能正常運作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:17:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而如果沒有尼爾瓦修 我們就沒法完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道什麼使命不使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那為什麼 為什麼你在這裡救了梅特爾她們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是全盤相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你之所以脫離軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為不想再奉命去殺害無辜的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼使命不使命的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣不是和聽命於軍隊沒有任何區別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡 你在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不願意見到無辜的人被殺害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論用怎樣的形式都想贖罪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在出去的話 會給霍蘭德他們添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓 你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開尼爾瓦修去阻止軍隊的轟炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能對提普特裡老婆婆她們見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起來吧 優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明什麼都沒做 怎麼忽然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 蘭頓 尼爾瓦修說讓我服從蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼爾瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然導航不管用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是洞已經堵住了 數據可以在主監視器看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼辦 繞過塔的話可能就趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這兩座塔的中間穿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞到他們前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了 作戰結束 立刻離開這一空域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 2點方向出現不明機體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,型號不明的LFO正高速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LFO? 不是RPG麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對空炮麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這就是你們的決斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算前途艱險 但祝願你們的目的地一定充滿光明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞反應引擎 削弱反射能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是優萊卡的戰斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡 優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道麼 這裡據説是個讓所有人作出選擇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 優萊卡也一定在這裡選擇了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 提普特裡婆婆說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管這裡的外表怎樣改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡還是這裡 不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你當初在這裡作出的是個了不起的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且即使現在來看也同樣了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這地方不會改變一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你過去選擇了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也相信 你還是和當時的你一樣 沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從你來了之後 我可能變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 雖然不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那時我卻由衷地想為這女孩做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的選擇 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部責任都在我 那些全都是我擅自做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以優萊卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的滑空板怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是加工過了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 慌亂中丟失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在下一塊滑空板上裝上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這、這是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都聽優萊卡說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要帶著這輪子 你就是月光州的正式成員了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後可不准擅自行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保持整潔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這淩亂的房間是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 這是你的房間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這是你作為正式成員的首份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這房間收拾乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒變 我沒變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣麼 是這樣吧 是吧 尼爾瓦修
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了逃避過去的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光州駛向一切開始的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡和一名少女一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一項計劃正要展開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.30,0:24:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Higher Than The Sun
